{"tid":1317302,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"關於物資我有啲野想講","createTime":"2019-07-14T18:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T12:28:23.000Z","uid":189587,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b25f47db1a49a982ab1b9d016f41dcdf8270a8b9","tid":1317302,"uid":189587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:08:28.000Z","msg":"小薯仔成日執學校想講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（1）每次班房要咩物資大家都會好激動咁叫，結果會出現由一年級都運到上六年級既情況，結果積左好多物資係班房，有時班房比老師趕果陣趕住散，都拎唔切物資。<br />\n建議大家真係急切既先好嗌落一年級，一黎物資可以易啲分散係唔同年級，二黎重野有時同學仔唔洗搬得咁辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾件唔重但一袋既話就好撚重啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（2）如果傳緊物資上六年級時但六年級話唔要喇，可以三/四年級既每人都keep起啲，當一年級要既時候拎返都易啲，或者去到其他地方有同學要都有貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（3）有時大家臨放學見到有人漏底書包，可以幫手望下咩黎，再搵其他同學仔幫手散下拎啲返屋企，其他年級突然要用都可以拎出黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當然知道有老師查書包就危險既就唔好拎啦，但病左戴口罩，屋企有人受傷有鹽水係無問題架嘛！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw 多謝今日隔離屋比物資我地學校既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你同我都估唔到會有呢日，多謝你地支持我地！<br />\n至於扔濕紙巾落黎果個，我屌你老母臭化閪啊！"},{"pid":"04edde52772e576dbdc3ce76804437a559e59b84","tid":1317302,"uid":189587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:21:32.000Z","msg":"係學校拎左把膠剪返屋企做美勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚瘋狂剪紙先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a816966898e79186db21cf3b30b460e254b36b78","tid":1317302,"uid":189587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:31:15.000Z","msg":"最近開得多冷氣成日氣管收縮不停咳，唔知哮喘藥有無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65417e8dfe0b70150a524c5688f8f2799b3098c","tid":1317302,"uid":189587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:40:20.000Z","msg":"係學校做毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae709f93d686d7e16dc40ac2df7d4fd1a1d9f48b","tid":1317302,"uid":176349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:45:14.000Z","msg":"推！ 呢個真！好多時最後啲物資都係會浪費左！"},{"pid":"7e86996bde7270a8dc109606b358a1aba52f5e35","tid":1317302,"uid":258047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:46:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47abe2bec3f0af3b347c043553c1c1e46285c9e9","tid":1317302,"uid":80164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:56:24.000Z","msg":"六年級班房好多同學仔，嘢又多其實好迫<br />\n或者可以考慮多餘嘅嘢回傳比四年級幫手拎住先，要用嘅時候唔使再由一年級開始慢慢傳"},{"pid":"972e38ecef7348e595682e264243098f92a4dddd","tid":1317302,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:14:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c12aba9f35d99ccea068c673befb005cd66df0f","tid":1317302,"uid":189587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47abe2bec3f0af3b347c043553c1c1e46285c9e9","tid":1317302,"uid":80164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:56:24.000Z","msg":"六年級班房好多同學仔，嘢又多其實好迫<br />\n或者可以考慮多餘嘅嘢回傳比四年級幫手拎住先，要用嘅時候唔使再由一年級開始慢慢傳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T00:50:40.000Z","msg":"起身默默推～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都好驚迫到六年級啲同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 始終同學先最緊要"},{"pid":"3f545668605b5665e719ca6106c0e7c59bf3c06a","tid":1317302,"uid":189587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:38:18.000Z","msg":"拎左支生理鹽水返屋企，媽咪煮野食比椒彈到都可以洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e704f65e31d664bb9c56db383ba2f4102f6eceb4","tid":1317302,"uid":189587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s